        <num>2-7-8</num>
        <content>
          <p>The Commissioner may purchase all necessary materials, supplies, office and field equipment, and other things and may make such other expenditures as may be essential and necessary in carrying out this article, within the limits of the amount appropriated by law.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1937, p. 659, ยง 4.)</p>
